<item>
            <title>[FELIX-915] PackageAdmin returns null on getBundle(...) with system classes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-915</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When calling getBundle(clazz) on the PackageAdmin with a class from one of the system packages, the system bundle should be returned. In stead, PackageAdmin now returns null.&lt;br/&gt;
This applies not only to the &apos;standard&apos; system classes (e.g., BundleContext or PackageAdmin), but also to packages in org.osgi.framework.system.packages.extra.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
